p="1"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">If your order will arrive in multiple shipments, once one of those shipments has left our warehouse, the order status will appear as "Partially Shipped."</div></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-lj8dgqb8svh" data-core-is="block"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html" data-stopdrag="true" deep="1"><h6 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">Order Returned - "Returned"</h6></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-s404tkt24rl" data-core-is="block"><div class="ecom__element ecom-element element__text" data-stopdrag="" deep="1"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">It takes up to 2 weeks to process a return and credit your credit card account. Once your order has been returned and processed, the order status will show "Returned." We will notify you via email once your return has been processed.</div></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-71qcz0ju1li" data-core-is="block"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html" data-stopdrag="true" deep="1"><h3 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">Canceling or Modifying an Order</h3></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-4229opund9s" data-core-is="block"><div class="ecom__element ecom-element element__text" data-stopdrag="" deep="1"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">Before you place your order, you can view the contents and the total amount in your shopping basket.
